Cell C has launched a “revolutionary new” solution for users, called MediaPlay. The package allows “consumers to plan and budget for their connectivity and entertainment needs through one contract”, said Cell C. “MediaPlay allows customers to connect with the world and with friends and family, plus keep up with their favourite movies, series, sports, news, and music.” The package provides users with: “MediaPlay simplifies our customers’ lives by bringing them an all-in-one communications and entertainment solution through great value plans, whether on mobile, high-speed fixed 4G, or fibre,” said Cell C Chief Commercial Officer Junaid Munshi. This includes MediaPlay Fibre, MediaPlay LTE, or MediaPlay Mobile offers. The tables below shows the MediaPlay packages on offer from Cell C. Click to enlarge the tables.    